Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:48.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Good Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:49.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:50.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:51.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on your help again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.75,0:01:53.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're working hard as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:56.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm what's called\N"a poor man with no free time."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.67,0:01:58.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're early again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:02:00.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Morning, Mr. Gori!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:03.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Look, Mr. Gori, I've got good fish in stock today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:04.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Take a look at these.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:06.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,These are shore fish, red snappers!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:08.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So how about it? Wanna buy some?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:10.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,These are top quality goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:15.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Mr. Gori?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:22.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Darn! You've got a well-trained eye,\Nso you'll take the good ones again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:24.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So be it.\NGo ahead and take that with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:25.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How about this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:27.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:30.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Man! Got it. You can buy it for that price!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:33.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Gori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:36.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Got a bargain again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:37.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.09,0:02:38.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:41.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's the young man who joined Sakura Sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:42.55,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\q2\fnSweet as candy\b0\shad0\bord2\blur5\move(1110.253,365,-385.19,365,0,3960)}Currently showing "Sakigake!! Cromartie High School"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.18,0:02:42.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's a reliable guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:47.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Although he has a careless side, he's honest by nature, \Nso I look forward to seeing how it turns out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\fs52\c&HEFE4DE&\pos(501.88,144)\bord2\frz4.181\frx12\fry356\3c&H4C4C67&}Gorilla{\fnSegoe Print\fs62} Sushi
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gori, you're working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That reminds me, the chief was saying
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:04.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"I guess I'll try letting Gori make food for the employees for now."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.24,0:03:06.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:10.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.62,0:03:13.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What, you've already made a dish secretly?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's stewed food? Then I'll try it\Nand see how it tastes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:19.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You did a good job bringing out\Nthe taste of the leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.55,0:03:24.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The basics are the same for any kind of cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.39,0:03:27.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A good chef can cook anything well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.43,0:03:31.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In that sense, you may have a\Nnatural sense of flavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:32.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:33.35,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fnDFGKanTeiRyu-XB\b0\shad0\bord0\c&HA8B0B4&\frz321\frx16\fry4\pos(190.329,472)\clip(m 148.375 431 l 160.875 435 176.75 432 266.25 487 209.625 484 128 429 145 419)}Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:38.19,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\fnDFGKanTeiRyu-XB\b0\shad0\bord0\c&HA8B0B4&\frz321\frx16\fry4\pos(190.329,472)}Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You got a problem, dumbass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:38.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, like I said, the restaurant owner\Nisn't in right now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:39.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}All you gotta do is stamp\Nthis paper with his seal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Him again? He's an ill-natured landshark...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:44.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey! The restaurant owner is out.\NCome back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:48.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? I can't ask whether it's\Nconvenient for you each time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:51.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All things considered, you guys are strange,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,clinging to a dying restaurant like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:58.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, either way, you guys aren't in\Nany position to give me orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:03:59.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm the restaurant owner's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:02.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Gori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Gori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:06.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That landshark is my son...
