Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:14.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\q2\fnSweet as candy\b0\shad0\bord2\blur5\move(1110.253,365,-385.19,365,0,3960)}Currently showing "Sakigake!! Cromartie High School"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I believe I told you not to come here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:18.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You have no right to call me "Dad".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.03,0:04:24.91,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\bord0\shad0\c&H010304&\frx42\fry8\frz319.326\pos(439.57,203)}Contract
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You just have to stamp this document.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:29.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You'll be able to say good-bye to this red sushi\Nrestaurant and you'll make some money too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:31.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's not gonna be any\Nbetter deal than this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:34.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you still attached to the sushi restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:37.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Or is it humiliating to sign a contract\Nwith me, your own son?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.01,0:04:45.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is the second time you hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:49.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Only twice? I should have hit you more...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I still remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:54.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The first time you hit me was the\Nfirst time you sent me into the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:59.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You lashed out at me, saying that my way of washing the cutting board was crude or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:01.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You hit me over a little thing like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:04.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I think it was around that time\Nthat I started going astray...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Do you remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You went astray on your own.\NDon't blame it on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:13.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I put forth so much effort\N to make you a successful sushi chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:15.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I hoped you would\Ntake over this restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:17.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It is a child's duty to carry on\Nhis parents' wishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:18.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:22.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Such a fool. Keep saying that\Nfor the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll come again. See ya later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:25.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't ever come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you do, I'll throw some salt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:28.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:32.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\q2\fnSweet as candy\b0\shad0\bord2\blur5\move(1110.253,365,-385.19,365,0,3960)}Currently showing "Sakigake!! Cromartie High School"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:35.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mecha-ratta, mecha-ratta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:38.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That stupid old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.69,0:05:42.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're the one... from earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:44.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you new?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:46.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess I showed you an\Nembarrassing sight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:50.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, Dad and I have been\Nlike that for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:52.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We haven't had a decent conversation in years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:56.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When I was a child, I wanted to be a sailor,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I was denied without\Nhaving a chance to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:01.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He kept saying "you'll be a sushi chef."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:04.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's such a stubborn father.\NHe doesn't listen to what I say at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:09.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, there's no way we can face\Neach other with open minds now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:11.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\fnArial Black\fs52\pos(501.88,144)\bord2\frz4.181\frx12\fry356\c&H9DA4A8&\3c&H252C46&}Gorilla{\fnSegoe Print\fs62} Sushi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Geez, that idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.85,0:06:21.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Gori. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What the hell are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.19,0:06:25.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Banana sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:28.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Gori. Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:30.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's true that different ingredients\Nare popular these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:33.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but come on, bananas are just going\Ntoo far. Don't you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.20,0:06:39.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right, if I eat them,\Nit'll make you happy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:42.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sushi like this will probably taste so bad\Nthat I won't wanna eat it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:47.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I told you so. What kind of taste is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This tastes so bad that people can't eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:51.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:56.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I know you like bananas, but it doesn't mean\Nthat bananas are good with any dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:07:00.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If a chef forces something on others just because he likes it, he's not a first-class chef!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's a selfish ego...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Forcing what you like onto others...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.86,0:07:12.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's the same as me forcing\Nmy son to be a sushi chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:16.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Simply insisting on my opinions\Nwithout thinking about others' feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:19.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In other words, this awful\Nbanana sushi represents me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:26.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Gori... You made these banana sushi\Nin order to teach me that?
