Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:33.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\q2\fnSweet as candy\b0\shad0\bord2\blur5\move(1110.253,365,-385.19,365,0,3960)}Currently showing "Sakigake!! Cromartie High School"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:39.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dad... I really think I got my\Nstubbornness from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:42.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I used to rebel against your\Nstubbornness too, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:46.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When I think about it,\N I've become a stubborn dad like you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's already this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\fs52\pos(501.88,144)\bord2\frz4.181\frx12\fry356\3c&H252C46&\c&HB4B2AE&}Gorilla{\fnSegoe Print\fs62} Sushi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:50.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\fs52\bord2\frz359.669\c&H917D70&\3c&H5F4436&\pos(551.728,339)}Gorilla
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:51.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'd better get ready to open the restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:58.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I had a little time to spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:03.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'm just kinda fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I just tried cutting and trimming a fish,\Nbut it's pretty hard, it turns out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:09.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was impressed that you do\Nthis kind of work every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:13.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't get it... What the heck's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:15.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth,\NI got something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:16.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:17.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,banana sushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've seen this before?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:23.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That Gori guy... he gave it to you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.98,0:08:25.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, you too, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:28.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Humans are selfish beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:30.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They want to force what\N they think is good onto others...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:37.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, don't be so edgy. I'm like that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:41.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's probably why Gori\N gave this banana sushi to me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:43.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Like father, like son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:45.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My stubbornness is just like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.83,0:08:47.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:50.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I won't tell you to become\Na sushi chef anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:54.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and do as you like,\Nbut don't keep your current job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:57.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's time. I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:59.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Next time I cross this threshold,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I may have a buzz cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.56,0:09:04.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If that happens, help a guy out\Nand hire a kitchen helper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.56,0:09:05.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\fs52\pos(501.88,144)\bord2\frz4.181\frx12\fry356\c&H583838&\3c&H191528&}Gorilla{\fnSegoe Print\fs62} Sushi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:14.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So I owe everything to Gori, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:15.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that you two could reconcile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:21.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Listen, I told you before that I planned\Non opening a new restaurant, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll leave this restaurant to you eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:27.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I'm thinking about\N entrusting that new one to Gori...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.58,0:09:30.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? To Gori?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:32.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Let me hear what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:34.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:37.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There isn't any person with that much talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.06,0:09:44.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I feel that I can safely\N entrust everything to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:46.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Can I say one thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.69,0:09:47.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:51.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's true that he's excellent.\NHe's got a sense for sushi too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.36,0:09:53.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Although he has a slightly careless side to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,he's a man with first-class quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.65,0:09:56.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But he's a gorilla...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's not a gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:02.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's our family, no, more than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:04.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Do you judge him only by how he looks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.41,0:10:06.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:08.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Think how you'd feel in his place,\Nbeing called a gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Listen. I'll tell you one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's definitely not a gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:17.88,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.4\bord0\shad0\c&H2C272B&\fnGrimace\fs48\pos(598.177,388)}Tuna
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:14.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:17.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, it's too late today.\NI'll talk to him tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:20.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\fs52\pos(501.88,144)\bord2\frz4.181\frx12\fry356\c&H583838&\3c&H191528&}Gorilla{\fnSegoe Print\fs62} Sushi
