Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:26.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Morning! You're early, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, morning, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Chief!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:33.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Today's another fine day.\NLet's work hard all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, where'd Gori go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:37.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, if you're talking about that gorilla,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:38.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,he got picked up by the public health center.
