Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:36.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:41.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We think, in this show, we'd like to portray\Nthe dramas of everyday life from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.34,0:11:44.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Actually, NOT. This episode\Nwas a one-time thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:47.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was watching the whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:49.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I was watching too!
